	* contrib/m_whois.c: 
	- As pointed out by Lee, fix server hide 

2002-09-03 10:15  db

	* src/channel_mode.c: 
	- allow more than four "simple modes" i.e. +isntp but allow only 
	  one per. i.e. only one +i is allowed, only one -p etc. this
	  matches behaviour of hybrid-6 

