	* src/adns.c: Fixed buglet where timeout_adns would get readded to
	the event list on each /rehash 

2001-11-14 19:25  bill

	* Hybrid-team: 
	
	pro is dead, billy-jon took his place 

2001-11-14 06:33  androsyn

	* adns/internal.h, include/s_bsd.h, src/s_auth.c, src/s_bsd.c,
	src/s_bsd_poll.c, src/s_serv.c: Cleaned up the poll() loop so that
	it is really only using a single list now.  Also modified the
	timeout parameters for ADNS.  Added a flag to comm_connect_tcp() so
	that the caller can pass a timeout.  We needed this to reduce the
	timeout on identd checking, which is now set to a 10 second timeout.  

