2001-07-03 06:26  leeh

	* src/: ircd_lexer.l, ircd_parser.y, s_conf.c: 
	- quarantine{}; no longer exists.  its been replaced by: 
	
	  resv { 
	    reason="no services on this network"; 
	    nick="chanserv"; 
	    nick="nickserv"; 
	    channel="#services"; 
	  }; 
	
	  you can still list them by doing stats Q 

