2000-12-27 11:53  davidt

	* modules/m_invite.c, modules/m_lljoin.c, modules/m_topic.c,
	modules/core/m_sjoin.c, src/channel.c, src/s_serv.c, src/s_user.c,
	src/send.c: Massive bunch of fixes for LazyLinks.  INVITE now works
	if a hub is trying to relay an INVITE to a LL leaf which doesn't
	know about the channel yet.  TOPIC now works if a user on a LL leaf
	tries to get the topic for a channel the leaf doesn't know about 
	Hubs now only send MODE changes to LL leafs that know about the user 
	coredump in LLJOIN fixed..  some other misc stuff too...  

