2000-11-08 16:57  ejb

	* configure, autoconf/configure.in, include/config.h,
	include/modules.h, include/msg.h, include/parse.h,
	modules/Makefile.in, modules/m_admin.c, modules/m_away.c,
	modules/m_capab.c, modules/m_cburst.c, modules/m_challenge.c,
