1999-10-17 11:38  db

	* include/msg.h, src/client.c: 
	- removed (+) cruft as this was a Tanerism 

1999-10-13 23:27  tomh

	* src/s_bsd.c: Removed CONNECTFAST garbage, it was causing
	production boxes to load up on SYNs on the primary port and killing
	poll performance.  

1999-10-13 23:18  lusky

	* src/s_bsd.c: fixed m_ison to put trailing space on 303 responses 
	CONNECTFAST is always defined for USE_POLL now, was causing very
	  poor accept performance on heavily loaded non-Solaris machines using
	poll() 

1999-10-13 23:12  tomh

	* include/setup.h.in: put USE_POLL back in setup.h.in, removed
	stuff that wasn't needed 

